  <brief_title>Pool-based Exercise in Fibromyalgia Management</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pool-based Exercise in Fibromyalgia Management: a Prospective Randomized Comparison Between Stretching and Ai Chi</official_title>
  <sponsors>
